title: Hard Knocks Dallas Cowboys FULL SEASON S04E01-05
description:
I WENT THROUGH ALOT OF SHIT TO FIND THIS FOR YOU GUYS, SO A SIMPLE "THANKS" WOULD BE GREATLY APPRECIATED

HBO orginal series : "Hard Knocks"

Season : Dallas Cowboys

Episodes 1-5

(episodes differ in quality and file formats due to the fact that i had to hunt all over and get these from different places)


Hard Knocks chronicles the life of a pro football team in training camp. See what it is like to be a star on an NFL team while going through training camp, in comparison to being a rookie trying to MAKE the team. Witness the heartbreak of not making it, as well as the dream of becoming a star player for yourself. 

Truly a well done show and worth watching, even if you're not a Cowboy fan.


Don't be greedy,
            Be seedy!

Enjoy!
